GOVERNMENT OF INDIA (BHARAT SARKAR)
CABINET SECRETARIAT (MANTRIMANDAL SACHIVALAYA)
34
New Delhi, the 10th November, 2010
The undersigned is directed to say that with effect from the 10th November,
2010:
Shri Prithviraj Chavan relinquished the charge of the office of the Minister
of State (Independent Charge) of the Ministry of Science and
Technology; the Minister of State (Independent Charge) of the Ministry of
Earth Sciences; the Minister of State in the Prime Minister's Office; the
Minister of State in the Ministry of Personnel, Public Grievances and
Pensions; and the Minister of State in the Ministry of Parliamentary
Affairs; and
(i)
Shri Kapil Sibal, Minister of Human Resource Development assumed the
additional charge of the office of the Minister of Science and Technology
and the Minister of Earth Sciences.
(ii)
2.
The Ministry of Home Affairs may take further necessary action for issuing the
requisite Gazette Notification.
(K.L. Sharma)
Director (Cabinet)
